name: Product of two elements exists in array
description:
given a array,product of two elements in the array should exist in the array. elements cannot be repeated.

return the elements in a array

example 1 : given array is [8,11,6,100,88]

since 8 * 11 is 88 and 11 * 8 is also so return [[11,8,88],[8,11,88]]

if no solution found then return "not found"
